    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>For each US county, we calculated the probability of an ongoing COVID-19 epidemic that may not yet be apparent. Based on confirmed cases as of April 15, 2020, COVID-19 is likely spreading in 86% of counties containing 97% of US population. Proactive measures before two cases are confirmed are prudent.</jats:p>",
